hopobject.body: I came here to work anthonysfamilypharmacy.com Grammy-winning singer Alicia Keys and record producer Swizz Beatz vowed to make sweet music together for life in a weekend wedding in the Mediterranean. Keys and Beatz who are expecting their first child together later this year, swore their 'I do' in an island paradise ceremony led by new age love guru Dr. Deepak Chopra. The bride, who was raised in Hells Kitchen, wore a white Grecian-inspired Vera Wang gown and a diamond encrusted tiara. She carried a bouquet of purple calla lilies. Beatz, who was born and raised in the Bronx, wore a white Tom Ford tuxedo.
